Package edu.kings.cs233.fractal

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Fractory
    This class controls the generation of fractal images by displaying a menu and prompting the user for the necessary arguments for a specific fractal set.
    JuliaGenerator
    Instantiates an object to generate a Julia Set fractal image.
    JuliaPC
    This class calculates the number of steps before a pixel value is out of range.
    MandelbrotGenerator
    Instantiates an object to generate a Mandelbrot Set fractal image.
    MandelbrotPC
    This class calculates the number of steps before a pixel value is out of range.
    MandelbrotPCTest  
    MultibrotGenerator
    Instantiates an object to generate a Multibrot Set fractal image.
    MultibrotPC
    This class calculates the number of steps before a pixel value is out of range.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidGeneratorException
    This class defines the checked exception that is thrown to indicate that a problem occurred while generating a fractal image.
    InvalidValueException
    This class defines the unchecked exception that is thrown if PixelComputer.calculateSteps() returns a value that is less than zero, or larger than the maximum number of colors known by the ImageFile instance.
